<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About LifeVault</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #2c2f33;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      background-color: #36393f;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      position: fixed;
      width: 100%;
      top: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #7289da;
    }

    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #b9bbbe;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav a:hover,
    nav a.active {
      color: #7289da;
    }

    /* Main Content */
    main {
      margin-top: 80px; /* Space for fixed header */
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .about-section {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .about-section h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .about-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #b9bbbe;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .features {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .features h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .feature-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .feature-list li {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #b9bbbe;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .feature-list li::before {
      content: '•';
      color: #7289da;
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    /* Credits Section */
    .credits-section {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .credits-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .credits-section h3 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
      color: #7289da;
    }

    .credits-section p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #b9bbbe;
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      background-color: #36393f;
      padding: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: #b9bbbe;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .footer ul {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #7289da;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      color: #677bc4;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-section h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .about-section p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .features h2,
      .credits-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
      }

      .credits-section h3 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .header {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      nav ul {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      main {
        padding: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Header -->
 <header class="header">
    <div class="logo">LifeVault</div>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
        <li><a href="/signup">Sign Up</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main>
    <section class="about-section">
      <h1>About LifeVault</h1>
      <p>
        LifeVault is a personal life management platform designed to help you organize and cherish every aspect of your life. Whether it's capturing daily thoughts, preserving precious memories, or managing your finances, LifeVault provides a secure and intuitive solution to keep everything in one place.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mission is to empower individuals to live more organized, meaningful lives by offering tools that are easy to use and tailored to your needs. With a focus on simplicity and security, LifeVault is your trusted companion for personal growth and financial stability.
      </p>
      <div class="features">
        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li><strong>Daily Diary</strong>: Write and organize your daily thoughts and experiences effortlessly.</li>
          <li><strong>Memory</strong>: Store photos, notes, and moments in a secure, searchable archive.</li>
          <li><strong>Financial Management</strong>: Track income, expenses, and budgets to achieve financial goals.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="credits-section">
      <h2>Project Credits</h2>
      <h3>Abdul Mutlib</h3>
      <p>With 9 years of experience in Software Engineering Provided consultancy in this project.</p>
      <h3>Sir Ali Hassan</h3>
      <p>Software Engineer and Lecturer at IM Sciences, Sir Ali Hassan provided guidance and technical insights to shape LifeVault's Database.</p>
      <h3>My Fellows</h3>
      <p>Sana Ullah, studying at IM Sciences, contributed to the project's design and testing phases.</p>
      <p>Faisal Iqbal, also studying at IM Sciences, supported the development and feature implementation.</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <p>© 2025 LifeVault. All rights reserved.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>